latestPosts.caption:
Healthy lifestyle approach for me is ✍️

- NO TO ONE-SIZE-FITS-ALL approach as every body is unique and has different needs. Always go for a well thought, personalized strategy curated by medical practitioners. 📝What works for you, is your answer! 

- NO YOU DON’T NEED TO ADD 10 STEPS to your skincare. Minimal is always better (3 basic steps- cleanser, sunscreen, and a serum that suits you) 🤍

- NEVER APPLY A PRODUCT ON YOUR SKIN THAT YOU CAN’T AFFORD IN THE LONG RUN because once you stop using it, skin issues may worsen. 🙏🏻

- NO TO POPULAR TRENDS specially when it comes to eating and skincare. 
Go for fresh veggies and seasonal fruits always!! 🥦🥗

P.s: I’m not wearing foundation in this picture, it’s my natural healed self🌸
.
